DESCRIPTION:Contact Name: Laura Aunan<br>Contact Email: laura.aunan@esd.
 wa.gov<br>Workshop Language Option: English<br>Additional Information: P
 lease go to <a href="http://www.worksourcewa.com" target="_blank">WorkSo
 urceWA.com</a> and create your account prior to attending this workshop.
 <br>Event Registration: Sign Up Required<br>Approved Unemployment Insura
 nce (UI) Job Search Activity: Yes<br><br>Are you receiving Unemployment 
 Insurance benefits and considering enrolling in some additional training
  to enhance your skills or to change your career path? If so\, you will 
 need to apply for Commissioner-Approved Training (CAT) and/or Training B
 enefits (TB). This workshop will guide you through the requirements\, pr
 ocesses\, and research needed to submit an application.
